WEBVTT

00:00.976 --> 00:02.469
Last time on Star...

00:02.494 --> 00:03.968
You dance like a gringo now.

00:03.993 --> 00:05.741
There's a video of
GiGi and her aunt doing drugs

00:05.765 --> 00:07.290
- that's going viral.
- Alex, please tell me

00:07.314 --> 00:09.804
- you ain't put this video out.
- No, no, I didn't do this.

00:09.829 --> 00:12.269
- I don't even want to see you no more.
- GiGi, don't do this.

00:14.094 --> 00:15.606
Look, what I do want to talk about

00:15.630 --> 00:16.809
is taking Xander out.

00:16.855 --> 00:19.727
That's his guy Stephen
collecting suitcases from Mateo.

00:19.752 --> 00:21.850
Me and Carlotta's little boy,

00:21.852 --> 00:23.275
he never died.

00:23.300 --> 00:26.198
The first American
Sound Award nomination:

00:26.223 --> 00:28.125
Noah Brooks and Alex Crane!

00:28.150 --> 00:30.579
Best Pop Album:

00:30.604 --> 00:33.750
TAKE 3 for 3:31!

00:33.775 --> 00:35.124
When Star hears about the nomination,

00:35.148 --> 00:38.230
she's gonna explode.

00:38.255 --> 00:39.434
Oh, no, no, no, no.

00:39.436 --> 00:41.476
I just got on good terms with Carlotta.

