that away from you.

19:06.268 --> 19:08.944
Look who came to see you.

19:10.725 --> 19:11.999
Davis.

19:15.773 --> 19:16.898
Say hi to your mama.

19:18.323 --> 19:19.695
Yeah, there she is.

19:20.183 --> 19:22.801
We have to fight for
her, 'cause she can't.

19:23.391 --> 19:25.233
Yeah.

