never lay hands on you again.

23:58.948 --> 24:00.831
I promise you that.

24:04.977 --> 24:06.511
Thank you.

24:38.502 --> 24:40.161
Oh, come on, Pops.

24:42.813 --> 24:44.166
You've reached Bobby.

24:44.190 --> 24:45.290
Leave a message.

24:48.477 --> 24:50.545
I know, I know, I know. I got you.

24:51.164 --> 24:52.656
I got you.

24:55.539 --> 24:57.656
It's okay, we got through that.

24:58.221 --> 24:59.712
We got through that.

24:59.739 --> 25:01.914
Shh.

25:40.259 --> 25:42.826
And just heal her, Lord,
and bring her home to us.

25:43.532 --> 25:45.783
In Jesus's name, amen.

25:45.944 --> 25:47.227
Amen.

25:49.848 --> 25:51.089
I don't get it. How do you pray

25:51.114 --> 25:53.564
to a God that would even
allow her to be in that bed?

25:55.103 --> 25:56.252
It's the same God

25:56.277 --> 25:58.275
that allowed Derek to
get up out that chair.

25:59.465 --> 26:03.624
The same God that kept
you through a plane crash.

26:08.015 --> 26:10.646
The same God that gives
us chance after chance.

26:11.842 --> 26:13.692
We just got to reach
out there and grab 'em.

26:14.326 --> 26:16.471
Because life can change
in the blink of an eye,

26:16.496 --> 26:20.264
so you got to go for
what you want. Today.

26:21.094 --> 26:22.469
Ain't no point in waiting.

26:49.074 --> 26:53.051
You know, when I was looking
at Star in that hospital bed,

26:54.272 --> 26:55.937
I thought about you and Xander.

26:56.779 --> 26:58.596
That could be your ass laying there.

26:59.074 --> 27:01.190
He will never lay hands on me again.

27:01.215 --> 27:03.596
Yeah, until he come up

27:03.621 --> 27:05.958
with some clever little words
and you forgive him again.

27:06.457 --> 27:07.574
Not this time.

27:08.418 --> 27:11.312
Look, I'm really ready to start
the next chapter in my life.

27:12.245 --> 27:15.062
And I can't do that constantly
looking over my damn shoulder.

27:15.545 --> 27:16.643
So what you gonna do?

27:16.668 --> 27:17.784
Confront him.

27:18.494 --> 27:21.217
You name the time and the place

27:22.444 --> 27:23.545
and I'll be there.

27:25.538 --> 27:26.835
I will.

27:29.180 --> 27:30.406
I promise.

27:36.206 --> 27:38.553
Don't get too lit.

27:38.578 --> 27:39.994
Mm.

27:40.019 --> 27:41.963
I need to get to the nomination party.

28:08.361 --> 28:10.022
Alex, this way!

28:14.677 --> 28:16.761
When are new songs
from Gravity coming out?

28:19.226 --> 28:20.733
Someone looks happy.

28:20.758 --> 28:23.328
Well, I just locked down a
deal with the Jaramillo brothers

28:23.353 --> 28:25.170
