28:25.195 --> 28:26.693
Of course I'm going to be excited.

28:26.718 --> 28:28.510
Alex, looking good.

28:28.535 --> 28:31.186
- You know what, I was talking today to Carlotta.
- Yeah?

28:31.211 --> 28:34.289
She reminded me that sometimes
you have to stop outsourcing

28:34.314 --> 28:36.489
- and go back to my roots.
- Oh.

28:36.514 --> 28:37.997
Sounds like a smart woman.

28:38.170 --> 28:39.278
