28:44.840 --> 28:45.889
No, I didn't.

28:45.914 --> 28:46.983
Trust me.

28:53.349 --> 28:55.549
GiGi! Just two days
after your aunt's suicide?

28:56.495 --> 28:58.749
GiGi, were you the one to
find your aunt's dead body?

28:58.774 --> 29:00.736
What was so bad
that it made her kill herself?

29:00.760 --> 29:01.840
Did you do something?

29:01.865 --> 29:03.571
Get the hell out of here!

29:04.642 --> 29:06.718
Oh, no...

29:07.146 --> 29:09.571
How does it feel knowing
she just gave up, GiGi?

29:09.596 --> 29:11.424
