- GiGi, one more!

29:12.742 --> 29:14.134
Come on, GiGi.

29:16.316 --> 29:18.558
♪ My G, I've been on one on my solo ♪

29:18.583 --> 29:20.444
♪ Only know how to show me... ♪

29:22.400 --> 29:23.893
