29:25.403 --> 29:27.729
How could she not know
how much I loved her?

29:38.670 --> 29:40.397
Look, I know you're hurting.

29:40.422 --> 29:41.472
You don't get it.

29:42.444 --> 29:44.752
She was the closest
thing I had to a mother.

29:45.211 --> 29:46.719
I pushed her to this.

29:46.868 --> 29:48.955
If I hadn't of fired
her, she'd still be alive.

29:49.889 --> 29:51.789
I shouldn't have did that video.

29:52.081 --> 29:53.714
If you think this the first time that

29:53.739 --> 29:55.548
Aunt Ginny's druguse has been outed,

29:55.573 --> 29:56.674
you're crazy.

29:56.699 --> 29:57.882
Okay, everybody knew.

30:01.130 --> 30:02.613
I'm sorry if I ever blamed you.

30:04.960 --> 30:06.300
GiGi, look at me.

30:06.325 --> 30:07.500
Look at me.

30:08.163 --> 30:11.663
What happened to your
aunt is not your fault.

30:12.176 --> 30:13.546
I had to learn that lesson.

30:13.571 --> 30:15.789
Hell, I'm still trying
to learn it with my mom.

30:21.852 --> 30:23.329
She pulled the trigger...

30:26.699 --> 30:28.284
