32:12.321 --> 32:14.105
♪ I've been giving all of me ♪

32:14.107 --> 32:17.099
♪ You've been giving none of you ♪

32:17.101 --> 32:19.192
♪ It's feeling like eternity ♪

32:19.217 --> 32:22.251
♪ Somebody tell me what to do ♪

32:23.533 --> 32:24.745
Noah.

32:25.305 --> 32:27.069
Noah, what is this?!

32:27.094 --> 32:30.279
♪ So sick of love ♪

32:30.439 --> 32:31.852
