32:47.267 --> 32:48.508
Okay. Okay.

32:48.533 --> 32:49.675
♪ Die alone ♪

32:52.840 --> 32:54.523
- ♪ Than to keep loving you ♪
- What?

32:54.752 --> 32:55.784
Davis.

32:59.710 --> 33:02.361
Bitch, you better get off that
phone and go get to the front.

33:02.386 --> 33:04.061
You know we got work to do.

33:04.574 --> 33:06.014
Girl.

33:06.016 --> 33:07.749
♪ I don't care about who's snitching ♪

33:07.751 --> 33:09.914
♪ Only care about my business,
