34:39.385 --> 34:40.900
'cause I loved you.

34:42.313 --> 34:43.577
I love you.

34:43.601 --> 34:44.891
I hate you. Back up.

34:44.917 --> 34:46.210
You sorry.

34:46.235 --> 34:47.510
You ain't no real man,

34:47.534 --> 34:49.418
taking no real responsibility.

34:50.750 --> 34:52.429
