36:16.839 --> 36:19.800
I want Davis full-time
with me until Star wakes up.

36:19.940 --> 36:21.862
Simone, that's a lot of responsibility.

36:22.354 --> 36:24.464
That's a whole child. Are
you sure you want that?

36:24.489 --> 36:26.182
I've already talked about it with Angel.

36:27.426 --> 36:29.720
I'd rather have this baby
with me than in the system.

36:34.091 --> 36:35.975
Yeah.

36:43.968 --> 36:46.088
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

36:46.637 --> 36:48.478
Where's Davis? Davis?

36:48.639 --> 36:50.798
Simone came to get him.

36:50.823 --> 36:52.205
He's safe.

36:52.230 --> 36:53.816
